re</a> , who have received their first BRIT nominations in over three decades for <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">&#39;Songs Of A Lost World&#39;</a> – they are up for Album Of The Year, Group Of The Year and Alt/Rock Act. <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">The Beatles</a> have also been nominated for the Song Of The Year with Mastercard for <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">&#39;Now And Then&#39;</a> – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">you can check out the complete list of nominees for the BRIT Awards 2025 here</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3825621" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825621" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825621" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robert-Smith-of-The-Cure.-CREDIT_-Jim-Dyson_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825621" class="wp-caption-text"> Robert Smith of The Cure. CREDIT: Jim Dyson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a