m/reviews/album/kendrick-lamar-gnx-review-3815647">&#39;GNX&#39;</a> cut &#39;Man At The Garden&#39; rose 260 per cent, as did his other Drake hit-piece &#39;Euphoria&#39;. &#39;Squabble Up&#39; and &#39;Peekaboo&#39;, both off &#39;GNX&#39; also rose 230 per cent.</p><p> SZA also experienced an 80 per cent jump in her streaming numbers in the US. </p><figure id="attachment_3836667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）和SZA在超级碗2025演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-sza@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836667" class="wp-caption-text"> Kendrick Lamar and SZA perform at Super Bowl 2025. CREDIT: Jamie Squire/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Both Kendrick Lamar and SZA are due to hit the road for a joint tour this year, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-and-sza-announce-joint-2025-grand-national-north-american-stadium-tour-3818353">performing across North America between April and June</a> . Shortly after their Super Bowl Halftime Show performance, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-sza-announce-2025-uk-european-stadium-tour-buy-tickets-3836665">the pair announced UK and European s